## Color Palette

### Primary Colors
- `purple-500`, `purple-600` - Primary purple
- `pink-500`, `pink-600` - Primary pink
- `indigo-500`, `indigo-600` - Primary indigo

### Accent Colors
- `blue-500` - Home navigation
- `emerald-500` - Search navigation
- `orange-500` - Reels navigation
- `red-500` - Error states and notifications

### Neutral Colors
- `gray-600` - Text primary
- `gray-500` - Text secondary
- `white/95` - Card backgrounds
- `white/40` - Border colors

