## Best Practices
- Use consistent gradient patterns across components
- Apply backdrop-blur for modern glass-morphism effects
- Use transform and transition for smooth interactions
- Maintain consistent spacing using Tailwind's spacing scale
- Use semantic color names for better maintainability
- Apply responsive design principles with mobile-first approach
- Use custom animations sparingly and consistently
- Maintain proper contrast ratios for accessibility